quran[75]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,Bͻ wo Wura Nyankopͻn Kokuroko no abodin
  87,2,"(Wo Wura) no a Ɔbͻͻ adeε, totoo biribiara pεpεεpε"
  87,3,Na Ɔyε nhyehyεε san kyerε (nipa) kwan
  87,4,Na Ɔma nwira mono fifire
  87,5,"Na Ɔma no hoa, na edwan"
  87,6,"(Nkͻmhyεni), Yε’bεkenkan (Qur’aan no) akyerε wo, na wowerε mmfi"
  87,7,"Gyesε deԑ Nyankopͻn pε. Nokorε sε, Ɔno na Onim deε εda adie ne deε asuma"
  87,8,Na Yε’bεyε no mmrε ama wo ama no ayε mmrε
  87,9,"Enti tu (wͻn) fo, efrisε mfasoͻ wͻ afutuo no so"
  87,10,Obi a osuro Nyame no debetu neho fo
  87,11,Na otibͻneni no deε ͻbεtwe neho afri ho
  87,12,Ɔno na ͻbεkͻ egya kεseε no mu no
  87,13,"Onnwu wͻ mu, na onnya nkwa nso"
  87,14,"Nokorε sε, obi a obedi neho nni anaasε ͻbεyε kronkron no adi nkonim"
  87,15,"Na Ͻbͻ ne Wura Nyankopͻn abodin, yԑ Sala (anaa ͻfrε Nyame)"
  87,16,Nanso mopε saa wiase asetena yi
  87,17,"Aberε nso a Daakye deε no na εyε, εno nso na εwͻ hͻ daa"
  87,18,"Nokorε sε, saa (afutuo) yi wͻ tetefoͻ no Nsεmpa no mu"
  87,19,Abraham ne Mose Nsεmpa Nwoma no
  88,1,Asεm kεseε a (nehuu) boro (nipa) soͻ no ho asεm no abeduru wo hͻ
  88,2,"Saa Da no, ebinom ani bewu"
  88,3,"Adwumaden, ͻberεhunu"
  88,4,"Wͻ’bεkͻ Ogya tanaa a, ano yε den paa mu"
  88,5,Yεbεma wͻn anom nsuo wͻ Nsuohyeε abura mu
  88,6,"Wͻ’nnya aduane nni, na mmom gyesε (nkasεε dua nyononyono bi a yεfrε no) ‘Doariin’ (na wͻ’bεweε)"
  88,7,"Ɛnnyε wͻn honam yie, na εmmee wͻn nso"
  88,8,Saa Da no ebinom nso anim bεyε frͻmfrͻm fεfεεfε
  88,9,Wͻn ani bεgye wͻn mmͻdemmͻ ho
  88,10,Wͻ Animuonyam Aheman no mu
  88,11,Wͻ’nnte nsεm hunu biara wͻ hͻ
  88,12,Asutire a εretene bi wͻ mu
  88,13,Animuonyam ahennwa bi a yama soͻ nso wͻ mu
  88,14,"Ne nhwehwε nkuruwaa a, esisi hͻ"
  88,15,"Ne mpikyi (anaasε atԑ anaa Kushin) a, yato no santen"
  88,16,"Ɛne kapεt papa a, εsesε hͻ"
  88,17,Enti wͻ’nhunuu sεdeε yasi abͻ Yoma
  88,18,Ɛne ͻsoro sεdeε yasi apagya no
  88,19,"Ɛne mmepͻ, sεdeε yasi de atintim hͻ pintinn"
  88,20,Ɛne asaase sεdeε yasi aterε mu
  88,21,"Enti tu (wͻn) fo, efirisε woyε obi a wotu (amanfoͻ) foͻ"
  88,22,Wonyε obi a wohyε wͻn so
  88,23,"Na mmom obi a, ͻbεdane n’akyi ama na w’apo (nokorε) no"
  88,24,Nyankopͻn de asotwee kεseε no bεtwe n’aso
  88,25,Nokorε sε Yεn hͻ na wͻ’bεsan aba
  88,26,Nokorε bio nso sε wͻn akontabuo da Yεn so
  89,1,Mede Ahomakye
  89,2,Ne Anadwo du no
  89,3,Ne (abͻdeε a egu) mmienu-mmienu ne Nea Ɔda mu Fua no
  89,4,"Ne εberε a anadwo befri hͻ akͻ, di nse"
  89,5,Enti nsedie wͻ woi mu dema mmadwemmafoͻ
  89,6,Wonhunuu sεdeε wo Wura Nyankopͻn de yεε Aadfoͻ
  89,7,"(Kuro) Iramfoͻ no, adan atenten wura foͻ no a"
  89,8,Yε’mmͻͻ wͻn sεso (anaasε yenni wͻn adan no sεso) wͻ asaase soͻ
  89,9,"Ɛne Samuudfoͻ no a, na wͻ’dwa abotan mu wͻ bonhwa no mu hͻ (deyε wͻn atenaeε no)"
  89,10,"Ɛne Farao, Asraafoͻ dͻm Wura, anaasε εpa Wura (a, na ͻbͻ nneduafoͻ wͻ εpa mu no)"
  89,11,Wᴐn a wᴐ’dii nsεmͻnee wͻ asaase no so
  89,12,Enti maa bͻne dͻͻso pii wͻ soᴐ no
  89,13,Wo Wura Nyankopͻn hwiee asotwe abaa-twa guu wͻn so
  89,14,"Nokorε sε, wo Wura Nyankopͻn tεhͻ rewεn"
  89,15,"Onipa deε sε ne Wura Nyankopͻn sͻ no hwε, hyε no animuonyam, na Ɔyε no adom bi a, ͻka (detu neho) sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn ahyε me animuonyam"
  89,16,"Na mmom sε Ɔsͻ no hwε na Ɔma neho kyere no wͻ akͻnhoma ho (anaasε Ɔma no hia no) a, ͻka sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn agu m’anim ase “"
  89,17,"Daabi (ԑnte saa), nanso monnfa obuo mma agyanka (anaa awisiaa)"
  89,18,"Afei monnhyε sε wͻ’didi a, wͻ’ma ahiafoͻ bi die"
  89,19,Afei modi awugyadeε adefodepε so
  89,20,Na modͻ sika ma no bro so
  89,21,"Daabi, sε asaase bubu na εyε gͻsͻgͻsͻ"
  89,22,Na wo Wura Nyankopͻn ba a Soro abͻfoͻ no ato santen
  89,23,"Na saa Da no yεde Amanehunu gya no ba a, saa Da no onipa bεfa adwen anaasε obetu neho fo, na deεn mfasoͻ na adwen anaa afutuo no bεyε ama no"
  89,24,"Ͻbεka sε: “Mehunuui a anka medii (dwuma pa) detoo m’anim maa me Daakye nkwa nna yi"
  89,25,Saa Da no asotwee a (Nyankopͻn debεtwe abͻneεfoͻ no aso no) obiara ntumi ntwe bi saa
  89,26,"Na sεdeε Obesi akyekyere (abͻneεfoͻ no wͻ nkͻnsͻnkͻnsͻn mu no), obiara ntumi nkyekyeree bi saa da"
  89,27,"(Yεbεka akyerε apapafoͻ no sε): “Ɔkra a w’akoma atͻ wo yamu"
  89,28,"San bra wo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ, W’agye wo atom wonso w’agye no atom"
  89,29,Enti bεka Menkoa no ho
  89,30,Na wura Me Soro aheman no mu’’